            Hint: The answer is no.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            Hint: The list begins <c>0</c>,
            <c>1</c>,
            <c>01</c>,
            <ellipsis/>.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            Hint: One answer is <c>00011011</c>.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>
            Hint: Find a bit string of length five meeting the conditions.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </subsubsection>
    <subsubsection>
      <title><xref ref="exer_relations_on_power_set"></xref> Select Answers and Hints</title>
      <p>
        Hint: Two of the relations have
        <m>\{1,2\} \sim \{2,3\}</m> and three of the relations have <m>\varnothing \sim S</m>.
      </p>
    </subsubsection>
  </subsection>
</section>